org.sd.match
Interface ConceptModelBuilderStrategy

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractConceptBuilderStrategy, FileLineBuilderStrategy
public interface ConceptModelBuilderStrategy

Strategy interface for building concept models.

Implementations keep track of state and respond appropriately to the requests for information, returning null when a part is finished.

Author:
Spence Koehler
